{"segment":3,"line_start":75,"line_end":164,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"可是，我们换个赌法好不好？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"换个赌法？怎么换？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"如果我也丢出三个六，我们就没输赢，对不对？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"那当然，我们这里没有庄家吃夹棍的规矩。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"这样我们是不会分出胜负的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"因为我是不可能失手的。","tone":"自信","chapter":18,"line_start":86,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"哦？你那么自信？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"当然，虽然你骰子穿了一个洞，分量已经轻了，但我还是有办法丢出三个六来。","tone":"得意","chapter":18,"line_start":90,"line_end":91},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"那你要怎样来定输赢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"我丢完以后，不但保证丢出三个六，而且还保证你也一定再丢出三个六来。","tone":"得意","chapter":18,"line_start":96,"line_end":97},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"开玩笑，我还会丢出别的点子吗？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":18,"line_start":100,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"我的意思是说，你除了三个六之外，绝对丢不出别的点子来。","tone":"淡然","chapter":18,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":108,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"假如你丢出不是三个六，就是我输了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":110,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"假如你又丢出三个六来，那就是我赢。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"少年人，你输定了。","tone":"大笑","chapter":18,"line_start":116,"line_end":117},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"笑是没有用的。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":18,"line_start":120,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"你们说是不是？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":120,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"你们要不要也来赌一赌？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":124,"line_end":124},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"有人","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"赌什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"赌我们之中，谁赢。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"有人","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"当然是钱老板赢了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"有人赌我输的吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"你们都赌钱老板赢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"众人","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"当然。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"那你们下注，我跟你们赌。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":140,"line_end":140},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"众人","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"真的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":142,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"真的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":144,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"你赔得起吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":154,"line_end":155},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"这够了吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"万一不够呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"有人","listener":null,"text":"如果不够，大家平分不就得了？","tone":"提议","chapter":18,"line_start":162,"line_end":162}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_huang_jin_da_ding","name":"黄金大锭","type":"special","owner":"char_zhao_wu_ji","one_line":"赵无忌用于下注的大锭黄金","description":"赵无忌从身上掏出的一大锭黄金，用以证明自己有足够的赌资赔付。","effects":[],"origin":"未知","rarity":"寻常凡品","related_characters":["char_zhao_wu_ji"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":158,"line_end":158,"text":"赵无忌掏出大锭黄金"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":165,"line_end":280,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"好，既然大家这么干脆，我也让你们占点便宜。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":166,"line_end":167},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"有人","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"什么便宜？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":170,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"我赢了，我只收你们押的赌注的一成。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"有人","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"我们还可以下注吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":186,"line_end":186},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"这个问题，你最好问问钱老板。","tone":"淡然","chapter":18,"line_start":188,"line_end":189},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"有人","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"为什么问钱老板？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"因为到时候赔钱的人，会是他，不是我。","tone":"得意","chapter":18,"line_start":194,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"你们尽管加注吧，不过，我看你只有这一锭黄金，赔起来未免太少了吧！","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":18,"line_start":196,"line_end":197},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"好，我再拿一样东西出来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":200,"line_end":201},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"好刀！","tone":"赞叹","chapter":18,"line_start":208,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"值钱吧？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":210,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"值。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"够赔了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":214,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"够了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":216,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"那就好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":218,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"你为什么不把这把小刀放在桌上？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":220,"line_end":220},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"我有用。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":222,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"你准备赖账吗？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":18,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"你错了，我是说，我要用到这把小刀，你既然可以用针，我当然可以用刀吧？","tone":"淡然","chapter":18,"line_start":226,"line_end":227},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"那当然。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"好，你们都下好注了吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":232,"line_end":232},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"众人","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"好了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":null,"text":"我要丢了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":236,"line_end":237},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"你输定了！","tone":"坚定","chapter":18,"line_start":282,"line_end":283},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"我可以告诉你，我再丢出点数是二个六，一个一，只有一点，铁输的点子，却变成了铁赢的点子，哈..哈..哈..","tone":"大笑","chapter":18,"line_start":288,"line_end":289},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"你把你的金刀也放下吧！我会替你赔赌注的。","tone":"得意","chapter":18,"line_start":290,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"不必急，我还没输呢！","tone":"淡然","chapter":18,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"你马上就会输的。","tone":"得意","chapter":18,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"看好了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":300,"line_end":300}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_jin_dao","name":"金刀","type":"weapon","owner":"char_zhao_wu_ji","one_line":"赵无忌随身携带的黄金小刀","description":"一把黄金打造的小刀，打得很薄，在灯光下闪闪生辉，发出黄澄澄的光芒。赵无忌以此小刀施展精妙刀法削去骰面数字。","effects":[{"type":"特殊","description":"可用于削切物体，极为锋利"}],"origin":"未知","rarity":"稀世珍品","related_characters":["char_zhao_wu_ji"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":204,"line_end":218,"text":"赵无忌掏出金刀作为赌注"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":281,"line_end":390,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"看好了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":300,"line_end":300},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":null,"text":"很好！","tone":"大笑","chapter":18,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"果然高明，佩服！佩服！在下输得心服口服。","tone":"佩服","chapter":18,"line_start":340,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"等一等。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":346,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"还有什么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":348,"line_end":348},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"你不想翻本了吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":350,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"改天吧！今天手风那么差，再强赌下去，还是输的，这是赌徒要严守的规矩，对不对？","tone":"淡然","chapter":18,"line_start":352,"line_end":353},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"不错，你很懂得赌规，欢迎你随时来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":356,"line_end":356},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"我会的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":358,"line_end":358},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"还没请教你大名呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":360,"line_end":360},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"赌，只论输赢，又何必计较谁是谁？","tone":"淡然","chapter":18,"line_start":362,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_qian_lao_ban","speaker_name":"钱老板","listener":"char_zhao_wu_ji","text":"有道理，可是，交个朋友如何？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":364,"line_end":364},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"赌场无父子，我看也不必了。","tone":"淡然","chapter":18,"line_start":366,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_zhao_wu_ji","speaker_name":"赵无忌","listener":"char_qian_lao_ban","text":"告辞了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":368,"line_end":368}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_he_xing_hao","name":"和兴号","region":"蜀中","one_line":"钱老板经营的赌场，赵无忌在此与钱老板对赌","source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":32,"line_end":370,"text":"赵无忌在和兴号与钱老板赌骰后离去"}]},{"id":"loc_shi_shan_kong_di","name":"狮山空地","region":"蜀中","one_line":"狮山上的一块空旷泥土地，赵无忌与上官刃决斗之地","source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":382,"line_end":390,"text":"赵无忌在狮山找到一处空旷泥土地作为决斗地点"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
